行过袭击，之所以对其造成了破坏，是由于乌克兰经常在居民区部署重型武器和防空系统。俄外长：与西方的冲突正接近真正战争 俄前总统：世界面临第三次世界大战威胁"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-2833ec104e96cb78ea10b782cb8c34e2_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/580384989"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhfywxZ7r9aQ6EAMaCDkxMjU2Mzk0IL3uwZ4GMAo4/gJAKnIJNTgwMzg0OTg5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "43_1674663347.0961134", "card_id": "Q_580259310", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 73}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在你的家乡有哪些知名度很低，但实际非常好吃的「春节特色美食」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-06f5167b8f2ec4e7b1dae2f2de673822_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/580259310"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhfywxZ7r9aQ6EAMaCDkxMjI4MjI5IOzvvJ4GMAE4nAFAK3IJNTgwMjU5MzEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1674663347.0966105", "card_id": "Q_580031530", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 172}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《流浪地球 2》中是什么人精准预测到每次危机的时间？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "是地外高等文明？人类组织？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1f3d7a5412995f7883eae66821d6f474_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/580031530"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhfywxZ7r9aQ6EAMaCDkxMTc3NjY3IM+Ts54GMAQ4/gJALHIJNTgwMDMxNTMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4